. No specimens of this species were studied. 
<bibRefCitation author="Nielson, M. W." box="[762,931,1859,1885]" pageId="25" pageNumber="26" pagination="1 - 318" refId="ref38619" refString="Nielson, M. W. (1982) A revision of the subfamily Coelidiinae (Homoptera: Cicadellidae) IV. Coelidiini. Pacific Insects Monograph, 38, 1 - 318." type="journal article" year="1982">Nielson (1982)</bibRefCitation>
